{"type":null,"faqId":44117,"title":"为什么使用闪光灯拍照会偏色？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n.s2{color:black;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0006944in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0006944in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">皮套，手，手机膜等物遮挡住手机的摄像头或者闪光灯，会造成图像不清晰，整体图像偏色（偏蓝偏黄等）的现象，请注意不要遮挡。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">闪光灯打开与关闭拍下来的图像不一致，闪光灯的会略微偏黄，因为不开闪光灯时只有一种环境光源，开了闪光灯会有另外色温的光源出现，即多光源，是会有偏黄现象的，这个是正常现象，也提示您更新至最新版本。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">若出现闪光灯偏色，可尝试恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">有炫光与白雾出现，大部分原因是摄像头和闪光灯脏污引起，脏污会反射闪光灯的光导致出现白雾或炫光，请将手机壳取下，擦拭镜头再拍照尝试。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">注意，使用非标准手机壳时，即使镜头干净也有可能会出现白雾或炫光现象，请您尽量从华为官网购买专用定制手机壳。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9617","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400097000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":2,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"闪光灯,拍照偏色,偏色","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}